snippet.title: Exoprimal - Season 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Your survival journey is about to be uphanced. Beta variant exosuits, a Jungle map, a co-op Final Mission against a Neo Triceratops, and a co-op quest to slay a Rathalos from the Monster Hunter series await.
Happy hunting, exofighters.

#Exoprimal #Capcom #DinosaurOutbreak
